summary:
- **Early Escrow Release**: 30,123,526 shares (10% of issued capital) to be released from voluntary escrow on **29 July 2025**, ahead of the original 2026 schedule.  
- **Free Float Adjustment**: Post-release, free float increases to **72.4%** (217,339,909 shares) of total issued capital.  
- **Material Impact**: Removes potential double-counting in substantial holdings disclosure; Qualitas will no longer report a relevant interest in its own shares.  

*Omitted: Background on directors’ holdings, operational/FUM details (not directly material to liquidity event).*
